des:
Brown Noise has several tracks of mellow, relaxing, soothing white noise you can listen to when you or your baby are having a hard time sleeping.

Just open the skill, and one of the brown noise tracks will play continuously for 2 hours.

If you want to try an alternate track, just say, "Alexa next" or "Alexa, previous" to load another brown noise track.

Sweet dreams!
